<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">Our [total revenue](metric_name) reached [¥2.3 million](metric_value, origin=2300000, unit=&quot;元&quot;) in [Q3 2024](time_desc), representing a [growth of 18.5%](ratio_value, origin=0.185, assessment=&quot;positive&quot;) compared to the previous quarter.</span></span>
